   901→### CSS Layers Strategy
   902→
   903→```css
   904→@layer reset, theme, composition, components, utilities, overrides;
   905→
   906→@layer reset { /* Normalize */ }
   907→@layer theme { /* Colors, typography tokens */ }
   908→@layer composition { /* Layout utilities */ }
   909→@layer components { /* Button, Card, Modal */ }
   910→@layer utilities { /* Padding, margin, display */ }
   911→@layer overrides { /* Emergency fixes */ }
