  2188→```
  2189→
  2190→### High Contrast Mode Support
  2191→
  2192→```css
  2193→@media (forced-colors: active) {
  2194→  /* Ensure all elements remain visible */
  2195→  input,
  2196→  textarea,
  2197→  select {
