   148→
   149→### 1.3 Glassmorphism 2.0 (2025 Evolution)
   150→
   151→**Definition**: Translucent frosted glass effect with blur, transparency, and subtle borders creating depth through layering.
   152→
   153→#### Core Implementation
   154→
   155→```css
   156→.glassmorphism-card {
   157→  /* Semi-transparent background */
   158→  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
   159→
   160→  /* Frosted effect */
   161→  backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%);
