   676→## Part 4: Technical Implementation Guide
   677→
   678→### 4.1 CSS Elevation System (Production-Ready)
   679→
   680→```css
   681→:root {
   682→  /* Depth token system - sync with JavaScript */
   683→  --depth-0: 0;           /* No elevation (base) */
   684→  --depth-1: 1px;         /* Subtle elevation */
   685→  --depth-2: 4px;         /* Standard elevation */
   686→  --depth-3: 8px;         /* High elevation */
   687→  --depth-4: 16px;        /* Maximum elevation */
   688→
   689→  /* Shadow colors - theme-aware */
   690→  --shadow-color-light: hsl(0, 0%, 0%);
   691→  --shadow-color-dark: hsl(0, 0%, 0%);
   692→
   693→  /* Animation durations */
   694→  --motion-fast: 200ms;
   695→  --motion-normal: 300ms;
   696→  --motion-slow: 500ms;
   697→}
   698→
   699→/* Elevation Level 1: Cards, Tags, Badges */
   700→.elevation-1 {
   701→  box-shadow:
   702→    0px 1px 2px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.30),
   703→    0px 1px 3px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.15);
   704→  transition: box-shadow var(--motion-fast) ease-out;
   705→}
   706→
   707→.elevation-1:hover {
   708→  box-shadow:
   709→    0px 2px 4px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.35),
   710→    0px 2px 6px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.20);
   711→}
   712→
   713→/* Elevation Level 2: Buttons, Form Elements */
   714→.elevation-2 {
   715→  box-shadow:
   716→    0px 2px 4px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.25),
   717→    0px 4px 8px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.15);
   718→}
   719→
   720→.elevation-2:active {
   721→  box-shadow:
   722→    0px 1px 2px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.20),
   723→    0px 2px 4px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.10);
   724→}
   725→
   726→/* Elevation Level 3: Dropdowns, Popovers */
   727→.elevation-3 {
   728→  box-shadow:
   729→    0px 4px 8px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.25),
   730→    0px 8px 16px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.15);
   731→}
   732→
   733→/* Elevation Level 4: Modals, Dialogs */
   734→.elevation-4 {
   735→  box-shadow:
   736→    0px 8px 16px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.20),
   737→    0px 16px 32px rgba(var(--shadow-color-light), 0.15);
   738→}
   739→
   740→/* Dark mode adjustments */
   741→@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
   742→  :root {
   743→    --shadow-color-dark: hsl(0, 0%, 0%);
   744→  }
   745→
   746→  .elevation-1,
   747→  .elevation-2,
   748→  .elevation-3,
   749→  .elevation-4 {
   750→    box-shadow-color: rgba(var(--shadow-color-dark), 0.5);
   751→  }
   752→}
   753→```
