   807→### 4.3 Performance Optimization
   808→
   809→#### Hardware Acceleration
   810→
   811→```css
   812→/* Enable GPU acceleration for smooth animations */
   813→.element-with-depth {
   814→  will-change: transform, opacity;
   815→  transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);  /* Force GPU rendering */
   816→  backface-visibility: hidden;       /* Prevent flashing */
   817→}
   818→
   819→/* Limit backdrop-filter performance impact */
   820→.glass-effect {
   821→  contain: layout style paint;       /* Isolate rendering */
   822→  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);       /* Reduces blur on mobile */
   823→}
   824→```
   825→
   826→#### Mobile Optimization
   827→
   828→```css
   829→/* Reduce blur on mobile devices (better performance) */
   830→@media (max-width: 768px) {
   831→  .glass-effect {
   832→    backdrop-filter: blur(5px) saturate(150%);
   833→  }
   834→
   835→  .elevation-4 {
   836→    box-shadow:
   837→      0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15),
   838→      0px 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10);
   839→  }
   840→}
   841→
   842→/* Respect reduced motion preference */
   843→@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
   844→  * {
   845→    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
   846→    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
   847→    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
   848→  }
   849→
   850→  .glass-effect {
   851→    backdrop-filter: none;
   852→    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.90);
   853→  }
   854→}
   855→```
