    90→### Basic @theme Usage
    91→
    92→Theme variables are CSS variables that instruct Tailwind to generate utility classes.
    93→
    94→```css
    95→@import "tailwindcss";
    96→
    97→@theme {
    98→  /* Colors - generates bg-*, text-*, border-* utilities */
    99→  --color-brand-50: oklch(0.98 0.02 276);
   100→  --color-brand-500: oklch(0.57 0.24 276);
   101→  --color-brand-900: oklch(0.26 0.12 276);
   102→  
   103→  /* Spacing - generates p-*, m-*, gap-* utilities */
   104→  --spacing-xs: 0.5rem;
   105→  --spacing-2xl: 3rem;
   106→  
   107→  /* Typography */
   108→  --font-display: "Inter", sans-serif;
   109→  --text-xs: 0.75rem;
   110→  --text-xs--line-height: 1rem;
