   663→  .btn.rounded-none {
   664→    border-radius: 0; /* Utility wins */
   665→  }
   666→}
   667→```
   668→
   669→### Custom Utilities with @utility
   670→
   671→In v4, `@layer` doesn't hijack CSS cascade layers. Use `@utility` for custom classes:
   672→
   673→```css
   674→/* Simple utility */
   675→@utility text-balance {
   676→  text-wrap: balance;
   677→}
   678→
   679→/* Utility with layer placement */
   680→@utility text-pretty {
   681→  @layer utilities {
   682→    text-wrap: pretty;
   683→  }
   684→}
   685→
   686→/* Functional utility */
   687→@utility debug {
   688→  outline: 2px solid red;
   689→  outline-offset: calc(--value() * -1px);
   690→}
   691→
   692→/* Usage: debug-2 generates outline-offset: -2px */
   693→
   694→/* Utility with theme key resolution */
   695→@utility backdrop {
   696→  backdrop-filter: blur(--value(--blur-*));
   697→}
   698→
   699→/* Usage: backdrop-sm, backdrop-lg, etc. */
   700→
   701→/* Complex utility with variants */
   702→@utility card {
   703→  background-color: var(--color-white);
   704→  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
   705→  padding: var(--spacing-6);
   706→  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
   707→  
   708→  @nest &:hover {
   709→    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
   710→  }
   711→}
   712→```
   713→
   714→**CRITICAL:** In v4, cannot use `@apply` inside `@layer base` or `@layer components` without first defining utilities with `@utility`.
   715→
   716→```css
   717→/* ❌ FAILS in v4 */
   718→@layer components {
   719→  .card {
   720→    @apply rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md;
   721→  }
   722→}
   723→
   724→/* ✅ CORRECT - Use @utility */
   725→@utility card {
   726→  @apply rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md;
   727→}
   728→
   729→/* ✅ CORRECT - Or use CSS directly */
   730→@layer components {
   731→  .card {
   732→    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
   733→    padding: var(--spacing-6);
   734→    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
   735→  }
   736→}
   737→```
   738→
   739→### Custom Cascade Layers
   740→
   741→Create additional layers for fine-grained control:
   742→
   743→```css
   744→/* Define custom layer order */
   745→@layer theme, base, vendor, components, utilities, overrides;
   746→
   747→@import "tailwindcss/theme.css" layer(theme);
   748→@import "tailwindcss/preflight.css" layer(base);
   749→@import "tailwindcss/utilities.css" layer(utilities);
   750→
   751→/* Third-party styles in their own layer */
   752→@import "some-library.css" layer(vendor);
   753→
   754→/* Your components */
   755→@layer components {
   756→  .my-component { /* ... */ }
   757→}
   758→
   759→/* Emergency overrides (use sparingly) */
   760→@layer overrides {
   761→  .important-fix {
   762→    /* Beats utilities due to layer order */
   763→  }
   764→}
   765→```
