   767→## Container Queries
   768→
   769→Built-in support for styling based on container size (no plugin needed).
   770→
   771→### Basic Usage
   772→
   773→```vue
   774→<template>
   775→  <div class="@container">
   776→    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 @sm:grid-cols-2 @lg:grid-cols-4">
   777→      <!-- Responds to container width, not viewport -->
   778→    </div>
   779→  </div>
   780→</template>
   781→```
   782→
   783→### Container Sizes (Default)
   784→
   785→```css
   786→/* Available by default: */
   787→@xs   /* 20rem */
   788→@sm   /* 24rem */
   789→@md   /* 28rem */
   790→@lg   /* 32rem */
   791→@xl   /* 36rem */
   792→@2xl  /* 42rem */
   793→@3xl  /* 48rem */
   794→@4xl  /* 56rem */
   795→@5xl  /* 64rem */
   796→@6xl  /* 72rem */
   797→@7xl  /* 80rem */
   798→```
   799→
   800→### Custom Container Sizes
   801→
   802→```css
   803→@theme {
   804→  --container-card: 20rem;
   805→  --container-sidebar: 16rem;
   806→  --container-content: 48rem;
   807→}
   808→
   809→/* Usage: @card:*, @sidebar:*, @content:* */
   810→```
   811→
   812→### Named Containers
   813→
   814→```vue
   815→<template>
   816→  <div class="@container/sidebar">
   817→    <aside class="w-full @lg/sidebar:w-64">
   818→      <!-- Responds to 'sidebar' container -->
   819→    </aside>
   820→  </div>
   821→  
   822→  <div class="@container/main">
   823→    <article class="@xl/main:columns-2">
   824→      <!-- Responds to 'main' container -->
   825→    </article>
   826→  </div>
   827→</template>
   828→```
   829→
   830→### Max-Width Container Queries
   831→
   832→```vue
   833→<template>
   834→  <div class="@container">
   835→    <div class="
   836→      grid
   837→      @max-md:grid-cols-1
   838→      @md:grid-cols-2
   839→      @lg:grid-cols-3
   840→    ">
   841→      <!-- Collapses when container is below @md -->
   842→    </div>
   843→  </div>
   844→</template>
   845→```
   846→
   847→### Container Units (cqw, cqh)
   848→
   849→```vue
   850→<template>
   851→  <div class="@container">
   852→    <!-- 10% of container width -->
   853→    <div class="text-[10cqw]">
   854→      Scales with container
   855→    </div>
   856→    
   857→    <!-- Responsive calculation -->
   858→    <div class="p-[calc(5cqw+1rem)]">
   859→      Fluid padding
   860→    </div>
   861→  </div>
   862→</template>
   863→```
   864→
   865→### Container vs Media Queries
   866→
   867→**Container queries:** Component responds to available space
   868→**Media queries:** Component responds to viewport size
   869→
   870→```vue
   871→<template>
   872→  <!-- Container query: adapts to parent -->
   873→  <div class="@container w-1/2">
   874→    <div class="@lg:flex-row flex-col">
   875→      <!-- Changes at container threshold -->
   876→    </div>
   877→  </div>
   878→  
   879→  <!-- Media query: adapts to viewport -->
   880→  <div class="w-1/2">
   881→    <div class="lg:flex-row flex-col">
   882→      <!-- Changes at viewport threshold -->
   883→    </div>
   884→  </div>
   885→</template>
   886→```
