  1150→## Performance & Optimization
  1151→
  1152→### Lightning CSS
  1153→
  1154→Automatically enabled in production (via `@tailwindcss/vite`):
  1155→- Vendor prefixing
  1156→- Syntax lowering (modern → compatible CSS)
  1157→- Minification
  1158→- Dead code elimination
  1159→
  1160→```ts
  1161→// Disable if needed
  1162→tailwindcss({
  1163→  optimize: false
  1164→})
  1165→```
  1166→
  1167→### Content Detection
  1168→
  1169→Zero configuration. Automatically scans:
  1170→- All files (respects `.gitignore`)
  1171→- Ignores binary files (images, videos, etc.)
  1172→- No `content` array needed
  1173→
  1174→**Manual control:**
  1175→
  1176→```css
  1177→/* Include specific paths */
  1178→@source "../components/**/*.vue";
  1179→@source "../pages/**/*.astro";
  1180→
  1181→/* Inline content (safelist) */
  1182→@source inline() {
  1183→  /* Classes that must always exist */
  1184→  .dynamic-class-1
  1185→  .dynamic-class-2
  1186→}
  1187→```
  1188→
  1189→### Build Performance
  1190→
  1191→**Full rebuild:** ~200-500ms (3.5x faster than v3)
  1192→**Incremental rebuild:** <1ms (100x faster than v3)
  1193→
  1194→**Tips:**
  1195→- Use `@theme` tokens instead of arbitrary values when possible
  1196→- Minimize `@layer` complexity
  1197→- Leverage content detection instead of manual configuration
  1198→
  1199→### Runtime Performance
  1200→
  1201→All theme variables are CSS custom properties:
  1202→- **No runtime overhead** for theme value lookups
