  1399→    ${price}
  1400→  </p>
  1401→</Card>
  1402→```
  1403→
  1404→### SSR Considerations
  1405→
  1406→Tailwind classes work in both SSR and CSR contexts:
  1407→
  1408→```vue
  1409→<script setup lang="ts">
  1410→// Runs server-side and client-side
  1411→const classes = 'bg-blue-500 text-white p-4'
  1412→</script>
  1413→
  1414→<template>
  1415→  <!-- Classes applied during SSR -->
  1416→  <div :class="classes">
  1417→    Content
  1418→  </div>
  1419→</template>
  1420→```
  1421→
  1422→**Dynamic classes with hydration:**
  1423→
  1424→```vue
  1425→<script setup lang="ts">
  1426→import { ref, onMounted } from 'vue'
  1427→
  1428→// Safe: runs both server and client
  1429→const baseClasses = 'p-4 rounded-lg'
  1430→
  1431→// Client-only: starts empty, updates after mount
  1432→const dynamicClasses = ref('')
  1433→
  1434→onMounted(() => {
  1435→  dynamicClasses.value = 'bg-blue-500'
  1436→})
  1437→</script>
  1438→
  1439→<template>
  1440→  <div :class="[baseClasses, dynamicClasses]">
  1441→    Hydration-safe styling
  1442→  </div>
  1443→</template>
  1444→```
  1445→
  1446→## Migration from v3
  1447→
  1448→### Automated Tool
  1449→
  1450→```bash
  1451→# Requires Node 20+
  1452→npx @tailwindcss/upgrade@next
  1453→```
  1454→
  1455→Handles:
  1456→- Dependency updates
  1457→- Config migration to CSS
  1458→- Template file updates
  1459→- Variant order changes
  1460→
  1461→### Breaking Changes
  1462→
  1463→**1. No more `content` array** - automatic detection
  1464→
  1465→```js
  1466→// v3 - tailwind.config.js
  1467→module.exports = {
  1468→  content: ['./src/**/*.{astro,html,js,jsx,vue}']
  1469→}
  1470→
  1471→// v4 - Not needed! Auto-detected.
  1472→// Override with @source if needed
  1473→```
  1474→
  1475→**2. @import replaces @tailwind directives**
  1476→
  1477→```css
  1478→/* v3 */
  1479→@tailwind base;
  1480→@tailwind components;
  1481→@tailwind utilities;
  1482→
  1483→/* v4 */
  1484→@import "tailwindcss";
  1485→```
  1486→
  1487→**3. Configuration in CSS, not JS**
  1488→
  1489→```js
  1490→// v3 - tailwind.config.js
  1491→module.exports = {
  1492→  theme: {
  1493→    extend: {
  1494→      colors: {
  1495→        brand: '#3b82f6'
  1496→      }
  1497→    }
  1498→  }
  1499→}
  1500→```
  1501→
  1502→```css
  1503→/* v4 - global.css */
  1504→@import "tailwindcss";
  1505→
  1506→@theme {
  1507→  --color-brand: #3b82f6;
  1508→}
  1509→```
  1510→
  1511→**4. Variant order changed (left-to-right)**
  1512→
  1513→```html
  1514→<!-- v3 - applied right to left -->
  1515→<ul class="first:*:pt-0 last:*:pb-0">
  1516→
  1517→<!-- v4 - applied left to right -->
  1518→<ul class="*:first:pt-0 *:last:pb-0">
  1519→```
  1520→
  1521→**5. Preflight changes**
  1522→
  1523→```css
  1524→/* v3 */
  1525→::placeholder {
  1526→  color: theme('colors.gray.400');
  1527→}
  1528→
  1529→/* v4 */
  1530→::placeholder {
  1531→  color: currentColor;
  1532→  opacity: 0.5;
  1533→}
  1534→
  1535→/* v3 */
  1536→button {
  1537→  cursor: pointer;
  1538→}
  1539→
  1540→/* v4 */
  1541→button {
  1542→  cursor: default; /* Matches browser default */
  1543→}
  1544→
  1545→/* Override if needed */
  1546→@layer base {
  1547→  button {
  1548→    cursor: pointer;
  1549→  }
  1550→}
  1551→```
  1552→
  1553→**6. Border and ring defaults**
  1554→
  1555→```css
  1556→/* v3 */
  1557→.border {
  1558→  border-color: theme('colors.gray.200');
  1559→}
  1560→
  1561→/* v4 */
  1562→.border {
  1563→  border-color: currentColor;
  1564→}
  1565→
  1566→/* v3 */
  1567→.ring {
  1568→  ring-color: theme('colors.blue.500');
  1569→  ring-width: 3px;
  1570→}
  1571→
  1572→/* v4 */
  1573→.ring {
  1574→  ring-color: currentColor;
  1575→  ring-width: 1px;
  1576→}
  1577→```
  1578→
  1579→**7. @layer behavior**
  1580→
  1581→```css
  1582→/* v3 - Tailwind hijacks @layer */
  1583→@layer components {
  1584→  .btn {
  1585→    @apply bg-blue-500; /* Works */
  1586→  }
  1587→}
  1588→
  1589→/* v4 - @layer is native CSS */
  1590→@layer components {
  1591→  .btn {
  1592→    @apply bg-blue-500; /* ERROR */
  1593→  }
  1594→}
  1595→
  1596→/* v4 - Use @utility or CSS */
  1597→@utility btn {
  1598→  @apply bg-blue-500;
  1599→}
  1600→
  1601→/* Or */
  1602→@layer components {
  1603→  .btn {
  1604→    background-color: var(--color-blue-500);
  1605→  }
  1606→}
  1607→```
  1608→
  1609→### Gradual Migration Strategy
  1610→
  1611→**1. Keep v3 config for compatibility**
  1612→
  1613→```css
  1614→/* Load v3 config */
  1615→@config "./tailwind.config.js";
  1616→
  1617→/* Mix with v4 @theme */
  1618→@theme {
  1619→  --color-new-brand: oklch(0.57 0.24 276);
  1620→}
  1621→```
  1622→
  1623→**2. Load legacy plugins**
  1624→
  1625→```css
  1626→@plugin "@tailwindcss/typography";
  1627→@plugin "./my-plugin.js";
  1628→```
  1629→
  1630→**3. Migrate incrementally**
  1631→
  1632→- Move theme to `@theme` gradually
  1633→- Keep working JS config during transition
  1634→- Update one namespace at a time
  1635→
  1636→```css
  1637→/* Step 1: Migrate colors */
  1638→@theme {
  1639→  --color-*: initial;
  1640→  --color-brand-500: oklch(0.57 0.24 276);
  1641→  /* ... more colors */
  1642→}
  1643→
  1644→/* Step 2: Keep other config in JS for now */
  1645→@config "./tailwind.config.js";
  1646→
  1647→/* Step 3: Migrate spacing next */
  1648→@theme {
  1649→  --spacing-*: initial;
  1650→  --spacing-xs: 0.5rem;
  1651→  /* ... */
  1652→}
  1653→```
  1654→
  1655→## Common Gotchas & Edge Cases
  1656→
  1657→### 1. @theme Order Matters
  1658→
  1659→```css
  1660→/* ❌ WRONG - @theme must come before usage */
  1661→:root {
  1662→  --bg: oklch(1 0 0);
  1663→}
  1664→
  1665→@theme inline {
  1666→  --color-background: var(--bg); /* --bg not defined yet */
  1667→}
  1668→
  1669→/* ✅ CORRECT */
  1670→:root {
  1671→  --bg: oklch(1 0 0);
  1672→}
  1673→
  1674→@theme inline {
  1675→  --color-background: var(--bg);
  1676→}
  1677→```
  1678→
  1679→### 2. Can't Nest @theme in Media Queries
  1680→
  1681→```css
  1682→/* ❌ WRONG */
  1683→@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  1684→  @theme {
  1685→    --color-background: oklch(0.2 0 0);
  1686→  }
  1687→}
  1688→
  1689→/* ✅ CORRECT - Use @theme inline + CSS variables */
  1690→@theme inline {
  1691→  --color-background: var(--bg);
  1692→}
  1693→
  1694→:root {
  1695→  --bg: oklch(1 0 0);
  1696→}
  1697→
  1698→@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  1699→  :root {
  1700→    --bg: oklch(0.2 0 0);
  1701→  }
  1702→}
  1703→```
  1704→
  1705→### 3. @import Order Matters
  1706→
  1707→```css
  1708→/* ❌ WRONG - @import must be first */
  1709→@theme {
  1710→  --color-brand: red;
  1711→}
  1712→
  1713→@import "tailwindcss";
  1714→
  1715→/* ✅ CORRECT */
  1716→@import "tailwindcss";
  1717→
  1718→@theme {
  1719→  --color-brand: red;
  1720→}
  1721→```
  1722→
  1723→### 4. Dynamic Class Concatenation
  1724→
  1725→```vue
  1726→<script setup lang="ts">
  1727→// ❌ WRONG - Tailwind can't detect classes
  1728→const size = 'lg'
  1729→const className = `text-${size}` // text-lg won't be generated
  1730→
  1731→// ✅ CORRECT - Use complete class names
  1732→const className = size === 'lg' ? 'text-lg' : 'text-sm'
  1733→
  1734→// ✅ CORRECT - Or safelist in CSS
  1735→</script>
  1736→```
  1737→
  1738→```css
  1739→@source inline() {
  1740→  /* Safelist dynamic classes */
  1741→  .text-sm
  1742→  .text-md
  1743→  .text-lg
  1744→  .text-xl
  1745→}
  1746→```
  1747→
  1748→### 5. @apply with @layer
  1749→
  1750→```css
  1751→/* ❌ FAILS in v4 */
  1752→@layer components {
  1753→  .btn {
  1754→    @apply bg-blue-500 text-white;
  1755→  }
  1756→}
  1757→
  1758→/* ✅ Use @utility */
  1759→@utility btn {
  1760→  @apply bg-blue-500 text-white;
  1761→}
  1762→
  1763→/* ✅ Or use CSS */
  1764→@layer components {
  1765→  .btn {
  1766→    background-color: var(--color-blue-500);
  1767→    color: var(--color-white);
  1768→  }
  1769→}
  1770→```
  1771→
  1772→### 6. Container Query Naming Conflicts
  1773→
  1774→```vue
  1775→<!-- ❌ Ambiguous -->
  1776→<div class="@container">
  1777→  <div class="@container">
  1778→    <div class="@lg:flex-row">
  1779→      <!-- Which container? -->
  1780→    </div>
  1781→  </div>
  1782→</div>
  1783→
  1784→<!-- ✅ Named containers -->
  1785→<div class="@container/outer">
  1786→  <div class="@container/inner">
  1787→    <div class="@lg/outer:flex-row">
  1788→      <!-- Explicit -->
  1789→    </div>
  1790→  </div>
  1791→</div>
  1792→```
  1793→
  1794→### 7. Dark Mode with @theme inline
  1795→
  1796→```css
  1797→/* ❌ Won't work - hardcoded value */
  1798→@theme inline {
  1799→  --color-background: oklch(1 0 0);
  1800→}
  1801→
  1802→.dark {
  1803→  --color-background: oklch(0.2 0 0); /* No effect */
  1804→}
  1805→
  1806→/* ✅ Use indirection */
  1807→@theme inline {
  1808→  --color-background: var(--bg);
  1809→}
  1810→
  1811→:root {
  1812→  --bg: oklch(1 0 0);
  1813→}
  1814→
  1815→.dark {
  1816→  --bg: oklch(0.2 0 0);
  1817→}
  1818→```
  1819→
  1820→### 8. Third-Party CSS with @layer
  1821→
  1822→```css
  1823→/* ❌ Imports third-party CSS with @layer base */
  1824→@import "some-library.css";
  1825→
  1826→/* Error: no matching @tailwind base directive */
  1827→
  1828→/* ✅ Use layer() syntax */
  1829→@layer theme, base, vendor, utilities;
  1830→
  1831→@import "tailwindcss/theme.css" layer(theme);
  1832→@import "tailwindcss/preflight.css" layer(base);
  1833→@import "some-library.css" layer(vendor);
  1834→@import "tailwindcss/utilities.css" layer(utilities);
  1835→```
  1836→
  1837→### 9. Arbitrary Values with Theme Variables
  1838→
  1839→```vue
  1840→<template>
  1841→  <!-- ❌ Wrong syntax -->
  1842→  <div class="text-[--color-brand-500]" />
  1843→  
  1844→  <!-- ✅ Correct -->
  1845→  <div class="text-[var(--color-brand-500)]" />
  1846→  
  1847→  <!-- ✅ Better - use utility directly -->
  1848→  <div class="text-brand-500" />
  1849→</template>
  1850→```
  1851→
  1852→### 10. SSR Hydration with Dynamic Classes
  1853→
  1854→```vue
  1855→<script setup lang="ts">
  1856→import { ref, onMounted } from 'vue'
  1857→
  1858→// ❌ Causes hydration mismatch
  1859→const classes = ref(
  1860→  typeof window !== 'undefined' 
  1861→    ? 'client-class' 
  1862→    : 'server-class'
  1863→)
  1864→
  1865→// ✅ Defer client-only classes to onMounted
  1866→const classes = ref('server-class')
  1867→
  1868→onMounted(() => {
  1869→  classes.value = 'client-class'
  1870→})
  1871→</script>
  1872→```
  1873→
  1874→## Best Practices
  1875→
  1876→### 1. Prefer @theme for Scalability
  1877→
  1878→```css
  1879→/* ✅ Maintainable */
  1880→@theme {
  1881→  --color-primary: oklch(0.57 0.24 276);
  1882→  --color-secondary: oklch(0.55 0.22 240);
  1883→}
  1884→
  1885→/* ❌ Harder to maintain */
  1886→.btn-primary {
  1887→  background: oklch(0.57 0.24 276);
  1888→}
  1889→```
  1890→
  1891→### 2. Use Semantic Color Names
  1892→
  1893→```css
  1894→/* ✅ Semantic */
  1895→@theme {
  1896→  --color-brand-primary: oklch(0.57 0.24 276);
  1897→  --color-brand-accent: oklch(0.65 0.28 150);
  1898→  --color-success: oklch(0.65 0.19 145);
  1899→  --color-error: oklch(0.55 0.22 25);
  1900→}
  1901→
  1902→/* ❌ Implementation-focused */
  1903→@theme {
  1904→  --color-blue-thing: oklch(0.57 0.24 276);
  1905→  --color-special-green: oklch(0.65 0.28 150);
  1906→}
  1907→```
  1908→
  1909→### 3. Document Theme Structure
  1910→
  1911→```css
  1912→/**
  1913→ * Theme Structure
  1914→ * 
  1915→ * Colors:
  1916→ *   --color-brand-*: Primary brand colors (50-950)
  1917→ *   --color-semantic-*: Functional colors (success, error, etc.)
  1918→ *   --color-surface-*: Background surfaces
  1919→ * 
  1920→ * Spacing:
  1921→ *   --spacing-*: Standard spacing scale
  1922→ *   --spacing-section-*: Layout-specific spacing
  1923→ * 
  1924→ * Typography:
  1925→ *   --font-*: Font families
  1926→ *   --text-*: Font sizes with line heights
  1927→ */
  1928→ 
  1929→@theme {
  1930→  /* Implementation follows... */
  1931→}
  1932→```
  1933→
  1934→### 4. Leverage Container Queries
  1935→
  1936→```vue
  1937→<!-- ✅ Component responds to available space -->
  1938→<div class="@container">
  1939→  <MyComponent class="@lg:grid-cols-3" />
  1940→</div>
  1941→
  1942→<!-- ❌ Component tied to viewport -->
  1943→<MyComponent class="lg:grid-cols-3" />
  1944→```
  1945→
  1946→### 5. Minimize @apply Usage
  1947→
  1948→```vue
  1949→<!-- ✅ Preferred -->
  1950→<button class="
  1951→  px-4 py-2
  1952→  bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-600
  1953→  text-white rounded-lg
  1954→">
  1955→  Button
  1956→</button>
  1957→
  1958→<!-- ❌ Avoid -->
  1959→<style>
  1960→.btn {
  1961→  @apply px-4 py-2 bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-600 text-white rounded-lg;
  1962→}
  1963→</style>
  1964→```
  1965→
  1966→**When @apply is acceptable:**
  1967→- Third-party library overrides
  1968→- Very complex, repeated patterns
  1969→- Generated/template code
  1970→
  1971→### 6. Component-Scoped Tokens
  1972→
  1973→```vue
  1974→<script setup lang="ts">
  1975→// Define component tokens as CSS variables
  1976→const cardTokens = {
  1977→  '--card-padding': 'var(--spacing-6)',
  1978→  '--card-radius': 'var(--radius-xl)',
  1979→  '--card-shadow': 'var(--shadow-lg)'
  1980→}
  1981→</script>
  1982→
  1983→<template>
  1984→  <div 
  1985→    :style="cardTokens"
  1986→    class="p-[--card-padding] rounded-[--card-radius] shadow-[--card-shadow]"
  1987→  >
  1988→    <slot />
  1989→  </div>
  1990→</template>
  1991→```
  1992→
  1993→### 7. Type-Safe Variant Patterns
  1994→
  1995→```ts
  1996→// utils/variants.ts
  1997→export const buttonVariants = {
  1998→  variant: {
  1999→    primary: 'bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-600 text-white',
  2000→    secondary: 'bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 text-gray-900',
  2001→    ghost: 'hover:bg-gray-100'
