  2031→
  2032→### 9. Organize Utilities by Function
  2033→
  2034→```css
  2035→@import "tailwindcss";
  2036→
  2037→/* Design tokens */
  2038→@theme { /* ... */ }
  2039→
  2040→/* Base styles */
