Arbitrary values bypass design system consistency.

### 2. Scoped Styles (Anti-pattern)

**❌ Wrong:**
```vue
<style scoped>
.my-button {
  @apply px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500;
}
</style>
```

**✅ Right:**
```html
