## 4. Dark Mode Implementation

### Dual Pattern Approach (design-system.css:164-178, 376-430)

**Method 1: Semantic color overrides**
```css
/* Light mode defaults in :root */
--color-surface-primary: #ffffff;
--color-surface-secondary: var(--color-gray-50);
--color-text-primary: var(--color-gray-900);

/* Dark mode overrides via [data-theme="dark"] */
[data-theme="dark"] {
  --color-surface-primary: var(--color-gray-800);
  --color-surface-secondary: var(--color-gray-900);
  --color-text-primary: var(--color-gray-100);
}
