**Method 2: CSS custom variant (global.css:12)**
```css
@custom-variant dark (&:where([data-theme=dark], [data-theme=dark] *));
```

This enables Tailwind-like syntax:
```css
bg-white dark:bg-gray-800
text-gray-900 dark:text-white
```

