### Modern Depth System (utilities.css:502-840)

**Layered Shadow System (Ambient + Contact):**

```css
.shadow-depth-1 {
  box-shadow:
    0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06),    /* contact shadow - close */
    0px 0px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);    /* ambient shadow - diffuse */
}

.shadow-depth-2 {
  box-shadow:
    0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08),
    0px 0px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
}

.shadow-depth-4, .shadow-depth-6, .shadow-depth-8,
.shadow-depth-12, .shadow-depth-16, .shadow-depth-24 {
  /* Progressive scaling of contact + ambient shadows */
}

/* Dark mode shadows 3-4x stronger for visibility */
[data-theme="dark"] .shadow-depth-1 {
  box-shadow:
    0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.30),
    0px 0px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.40);
}
```

**Color-Matched Shadows (Using OKLCH):**
```css
.shadow-primary {
  box-shadow:
    0px 4px 12px oklch(50% 0.16 200 / 0.15),    /* Primary color shadow */
    0px 0px 4px oklch(50% 0.16 200 / 0.10);
}

.shadow-success {
  box-shadow:
    0px 4px 12px oklch(65% 0.17 160 / 0.15),    /* Green shadow */
    0px 0px 4px oklch(65% 0.17 160 / 0.10);
}

.shadow-error {
  box-shadow:
    0px 4px 12px oklch(62% 0.22 25 / 0.15),     /* Red shadow */
    0px 0px 4px oklch(62% 0.22 25 / 0.10);
}
```

**Neumorphism Effects:**
```css
.neomorph-flat {
  background: var(--color-surface-primary);
  box-shadow:
    8px 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12),      /* Drop shadow */
    -8px -8px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.70);  /* Highlight */
  border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
}

.neomorph-pressed {
  box-shadow:
    inset 4px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12),
    inset -4px -4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.70);
}

.neomorph-raised {
  box-shadow:
    12px 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14),
    -12px -12px 24px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.80);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}
```

**Advanced Glass Effects (Glassmorphism 2.0):**
```css
.glass-vibrant {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.70);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  box-shadow:
    0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);    /* Inset highlight */
}

.glass-frosted {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.50);
  backdrop-filter: blur(32px) saturate(200%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  box-shadow:
    0 12px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}
```

**Elevation Semantic Utilities:**
```css
.elevation-surface { box-shadow: none; z-index: 0; }
.elevation-raised { box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); z-index: 1; }
.elevation-overlay { box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10); z-index: 10; }
.elevation-floating { box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14); z-index: 50; }
.elevation-modal { box-shadow: 0px 16px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18); z-index: var(--z-index-modal); }
```

**Depth Layering:**
```css
.layer-back {
  z-index: 1;
  transform: translateY(8px);
  opacity: 0.90;
  filter: blur(0.5px);
}

.layer-middle {
  z-index: 2;
  transform: translateY(4px);
  opacity: 0.95;
}

.layer-front {
  z-index: 3;
  transform: translateY(0px);
}

/* Depth through scale and contrast */
.depth-recede {
  opacity: 0.80;
  filter: brightness(0.95) saturate(0.90);
  transform: scale(0.98);
}

.depth-advance {
  opacity: 1;
  filter: brightness(1.05) saturate(1.10);
  transform: scale(1.02);
}

.depth-transition {
  transition:
    transform 300ms cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1),
    box-shadow 300ms cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1),
    opacity 300ms cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1),
    filter 300ms cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

.depth-transition:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
}
```

